narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: German is a very fun language with a rich culture. I would recommend it.
It is a challenging course, but rewarding once you can start to grasp the language. I would recommend it because I know German is a useful language to know and an interesting culture to learn.
Yes and no. Depending on the other classes' workload this class can be very tough, however the learning benefits are great and fast.
